    "Small (n < 1, 000) probability samples are replaced by large and frequently updated datasets augmented via linkage with different sources.",
    "Consider these three examples of AI polling practices.",
    "(1) A polling company wishes to generate accurate granular estimates of political preferences and to present these to the public.",
    "They publish recruitment advertisements online and gather a large, individual-level panel, on the order of hundreds of thousands of self-selected respondents.",
    "Their political preferences are frequently surveyed."
